						               													<description>Immerse yourself in the conflicts of the Ancient World.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A great collection of classic and contemporary abstract strategy games is waiting for you to explore. As you discover what&amp;rsquo;s inside, it takes you back in time and around the world.  Travel to ancient Greece, through Assyria, then the Roman and Persian Empires, until you finally arrive by the great Yangtze River in the Middle Kingdom of China.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Unearth pieces inside the treasure chest to play popular and well-loved games such as Chess and Checkers (Draughts).  Discover Greek and Roman classics like Seega and Latunculi that are still being enjoyed in parts of the world today.  And as you dig deeper, you will also bring to light games with themes of ancient conflict created by contemporary game designers.   You can join the battle for Troy in ILIOS, sink Viking warships in Journey Stones, or expand your kingdom in Cartography. King's Ransom is a lighter chess variant with a prince, a bit of luck and a lot of bluffing! In Quorsum you race your horsemen home while obstructing your opponent's in a tile flipping, dice game. Kush offers a fast moving tile stacking game with an unusual twist: you get to move either your opponent's or your own tiles! Yangtze seems like a simple tile matching game until you  discover to master it both players need to think about the modern concerns of environmental conservation to prevent the river drying up.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Some of these games have also been offered as standalone box sets or Treasure Chest Jewels and some are only available is part of the basic Treasure Chest Crown Jewel. The Treasure Chest World Collection offers everything together with components for  11 classic and contemporary strategy games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game pieces are designed for use in multiple games, and can be stored in colorful handmade bags.  All the games have simple rules that take 2 minutes to learn and 10-30 minutes  to play.  In some games, the length and complexity of the game can be adjusted.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Decorate your living room with the Treasure Chest, keep it in sight at all times and entice your guests into a world of Ancient Conflict. Let this classic collection entertain you and create wonderful memories for your family and friends for generations to come.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
